    public class DatabaseWeightedTallyAlgorithm<ENTRY,WEIGHT,DAO extends InsertDao<WEIGHT> & GetDao<WEIGHT>,RESPONSE>
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.ashwork.upvote.domain.algorithm.WeightedTallyAlgorithm<ENTRY,WEIGHT,RESPONSE>
    An algorithm used to tally all or a specific subset of entries with some weighted association and return some response about the tallied results. The result of the supplied algorithm will then be persisted to some table containing the weights.

    1.0.0
